T1  - Banking on currency forecasts: How predictable is change in money?
AU  - Chinn, Menzie D.
AU  - Meese, Richard A.
JO  - Journal of International Economics
VL  - 38
IS  - 1
SP  - 161
EP  - 178
PY  - 1995
